trip_delay/60 as trip_delay_min
FROM completed_trip_with_delay

FROM default.surat_itms_live live inner join default.network_issue_regions network on live.route_id=network.route_id where weight > 2

SELECT traffic_delay.trip_id,traffic_delay.observationDateTime,traffic_delay.route_id,traffic_delay.trip_direction,traffic_delay.h3,traffic_delay.license_plate,traffic_delay.dwell_time,traffic_prediction.predicted_dwell_time, traffic_delay.primary_key, traffic_delay.geojson
FROM default.traffic_delay
inner join default.traffic_prediction
on (traffic_delay.h3=traffic_prediction.h3 AND traffic_delay.trip_direction=traffic_prediction.trip_direction)
where date_diff('minute',traffic_delay.observationdatetime,traffic_prediction.observationdatetime)<=0 AND date_diff('minute',traffic_delay.observationdatetime,traffic_prediction.observationdatetime)>-60

SELECT *,
trip_delay/60 as trip_delay_min
FROM live_trip_with_delay

SELECT DISTINCT observationdatetime, license_plate
FROM default.surat_itms_live live inner join default.network_issue_regions network on live.route_id=network.route_id 
-- where observationdatetime >=  ((date_add('minute', 330, localtimestamp)) - interval '1' hour)

SELECT *, 
MOD(CAST(time_slot AS int), 24) as time_slot_daily,
dwell_time/60 as dwell_time_min
FROM traffic_delay
